{"id": "1435478075516256379", "channel_id": "1326453691527594035", "type": 0, "author_id": "896400240192675850", "author_name": "hskzu", "author_bot": false, "content": "priority:\n>arith limit from murph (if didn't get early and you get poetic wheel and a murphy skill+strike can attempt to recycle into arith limit skill)\n>pollux cards\n>alva's + wheels\n>lone seed prioritized pollux/alva/horla (heal only) can skip murph since she's a sack and meat shield only\n>if opponent have cleanser snipe them with alva's charge+judgement\n>get pollux to exalt early\n>watch enemy dps behavior (if it's a helot with 5 charge dispel using pollux card, if it's a strike based unit use para, if it's just a pure dps delay their burst turn with weakness+vuln)\n>get enough sinmark spam to kill and heal\n>alva/pollux cleanup", "timestamp": "2025-11-05T03:57:23.096000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
